text: Nice that all sounds good! How did you shoot go? Did you get everything you need? It sounds like it will be a cool project! When do you have to get it done by?

It went okay, the weather was all over the place though! But yeah luckily I managed to get the shots I needed, the final project is due on 15th May. But I also have a deadline for a showreel and online presence next Friday!

Nice! Have you got a rough cut or something? I’d love to see where your heading with it!

Nice that a solid amount of time to get some nice shots done! How many shots have you got roughly do you think?

And ahh shit! That’s soon! If you want me to take a look at anything just send it over!
